two on a tower ( 1882 ) is a novel by english author thomas hardy,<ref>{{cite book|author=john sutherland|authorlink=john sutherland ( author)|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=qzj3ynvvqtuc&pg=pa643|chapter=two on a tower|pages=643|title=the stanford companion to victorian literature|origyear=1989|year=1990}}</ref > classified by him as a romance and fantasy and now regarded as one of his minor works .

19th century lit : bored lady constantine finds passion with an astronomer in--where else?--wessex in his " two on a tower "

thomas hardy